{"id":55861,"date":"2024-04-23T10:29:12","date_gmt":"2024-04-23T04:59:12","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/?p=55861"},"modified":"2024-04-23T10:29:15","modified_gmt":"2024-04-23T04:59:15","slug":"quartz-stone-for-kitchen","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/blog\/home-interiors\/quartz-stone-for-kitchen\/","title":{"rendered":"The Future of Quartz Stone in Interior Design"},"content":{"rendered":"\n<p>Quartz Stone \u2013 Transforming spaces, one surface at a time!<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>In the symphony of stones, quartz takes the lead, bringing luxury and durability to the interiors of your home. From <a href=\"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/blog\/modular-kitchen-interiors\/kitchen-countertops-options\/\">kitchen countertops<\/a> to backsplash, quartz stone has become a trend followed by every new homeowner looking to make a long-term, wise investment. Its popularity is not just a passing fad. The demand for quartz stone is soaring, reshaping how we experience our living spaces. Let&#8217;s dive in!<\/p>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">A Culinary Haven: Quartz Stone for Kitchen Platforms<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>The kitchen is the heart of every home, and quartz stone is becoming the canvas for culinary artistry\u2014especially on countertops. Quartz platforms offer durability and an opulent look. Plus, this stone impresses with its resistance to stains and scratches. With a spectrum of colours available, it easily integrates with various kitchen elements, crafting a beautiful kitchen.&nbsp;<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"940\" height=\"564\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/04\/23101916\/kitchen-platform-quartz-stone.jpg\" alt=\"Quartz stone for kitchen platforms, which offers durability and an opulent look\" class=\"wp-image-55867\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/04\/23101916\/kitchen-platform-quartz-stone.jpg 940w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/04\/23101916\/kitchen-platform-quartz-stone-300x180.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/04\/23101916\/kitchen-platform-quartz-stone-768x461.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/04\/23101916\/kitchen-platform-quartz-stone-50x30.jpg 50w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/04\/23101916\/kitchen-platform-quartz-stone-150x90.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 940px) 100vw, 940px\" \/><figcaption class=\"wp-element-caption\">Quartz stone for kitchen platform<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Kitchen Quartz Stone for Backsplash Goals<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Another excellent way to use quartz is on the <a href=\"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/blog\/modular-kitchen-interiors\/kitchen-backsplash-ideas\/\">kitchen backsplash<\/a>. This way, you can elevate your kitchen&#8217;s aesthetic appeal. The durability of quartz and its vast colour choices make it ideal for protecting and enhancing the walls. Create a seamless design flow, transforming your culinary space into a stylish and cohesive space.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"940\" height=\"564\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/04\/23101905\/backsplash-quartz-stone.jpg\" alt=\"Quartz stone for kitchen backsplash for a stylish look\" class=\"wp-image-55866\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/04\/23101905\/backsplash-quartz-stone.jpg 940w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/04\/23101905\/backsplash-quartz-stone-300x180.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/04\/23101905\/backsplash-quartz-stone-768x461.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/04\/23101905\/backsplash-quartz-stone-50x30.jpg 50w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/04\/23101905\/backsplash-quartz-stone-150x90.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 940px) 100vw, 940px\" \/><figcaption class=\"wp-element-caption\">Quartz backsplash- A stylish extension of your kitchen<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"mbgc-slide-caption\"><a href=\"#contactUsModal\" data-toggle=\"modal\"><img decoding=\"async\" class=\"img-fluid\" alt=\"Complete home interior solutions crafted with precision\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/04\/14224023\/complete-home-interior-solutions-crafted-with-precision.jpg \" \/><\/a><\/div>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">The White Quartz Stone (Sink too!)<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Clear quartz isn&#8217;t typically used as-is for kitchen platforms. In its natural state, clear quartz is often transformed into various colours, including white, black, and others, through a process called engineering manufacturing. During this process, pigments and resins are added to the stone, allowing for a broad spectrum of colours and textures. This engineered quartz is then shaped into slabs suitable for kitchen platforms!&nbsp;<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>White quartz stone is very luxurious and clean-looking. The platform easily brightens up your kitchen space. Check out this white <a href=\"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/blog\/modular-kitchen-interiors\/quartz-countertops\/\">quartz countertop<\/a> with an in-built quartz sink that offers a clean and airy feel, making the kitchen more spacious and inviting.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"940\" height=\"564\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/04\/23101855\/white-quartz-stone.jpg\" alt=\"White quartz stone for your kitchen for a luxurious and clean look\" class=\"wp-image-55865\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/04\/23101855\/white-quartz-stone.jpg 940w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/04\/23101855\/white-quartz-stone-300x180.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/04\/23101855\/white-quartz-stone-768x461.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/04\/23101855\/white-quartz-stone-50x30.jpg 50w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/04\/23101855\/white-quartz-stone-150x90.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 940px) 100vw, 940px\" \/><figcaption class=\"wp-element-caption\">Choose different quartz colours according to your kitchen aesthetics<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Black Quartz Stone for Kitchen Platform\u00a0<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Black quartz is the kitchen superhero that easily blends style and practicality. A smooth black slab in the kitchen with a matching quartz sink makes spills a breeze to handle. Thanks to its non-porous nature, the dark stone ensures a hygienic and odour-free cooking experience, allowing you to cook with confidence. And let\u2019s not forget this dark colour brings drama while quartz brings luxury. Usher in a stunning kitchen transformation with a gorgeous black quartz countertop!<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"940\" height=\"564\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/04\/23101845\/black-quartz-stone.jpg\" alt=\"Black quartz stone for kitchen platform, which is a blend of style and practicality\" class=\"wp-image-55864\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/04\/23101845\/black-quartz-stone.jpg 940w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/04\/23101845\/black-quartz-stone-300x180.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/04\/23101845\/black-quartz-stone-768x461.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/04\/23101845\/black-quartz-stone-50x30.jpg 50w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/04\/23101845\/black-quartz-stone-150x90.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 940px) 100vw, 940px\" \/><figcaption class=\"wp-element-caption\">The bold elegance of black<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Quartz Stone Benefits\u00a0<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<ul class=\"wp-block-list\">\n<li><strong>Aesthetics<\/strong>: With a broad spectrum of colours and patterns, create a luxurious and visually appealing cooking space.<\/li>\n\n\n\n<li><strong>Durability<\/strong>: This stone is highly resistant to stains and scratches.<\/li>\n\n\n\n<li><strong>Hygienic Surface:<\/strong> Non-porous nature ensures a clean and germ-free environment, which is ideal for food preparation areas.&nbsp;<\/li>\n\n\n\n<li><strong>Integration<\/strong>: Easily integrates into various kitchen elements, fostering a cohesive design.<\/li>\n\n\n\n<li><strong>Maintenance<\/strong>: Wipe away spills effortlessly without worrying about long-term damage.<\/li>\n\n\n\n<li><strong>Heat and Scratch Resistance: Withstand high temperatures, making it suitable near stovetops.<\/strong><\/li>\n\n\n\n<li><strong>Increased Home Value: Quartz adds value to your home, making it an attractive feature for potential buyers.<\/strong><\/li>\n<\/ul>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"940\" height=\"564\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/04\/23101835\/quartz-stone-benefits.jpg\" alt=\"Benefits of quartz stone for your luxurious kitchen aesthetics\" class=\"wp-image-55863\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/04\/23101835\/quartz-stone-benefits.jpg 940w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/04\/23101835\/quartz-stone-benefits-300x180.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/04\/23101835\/quartz-stone-benefits-768x461.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/04\/23101835\/quartz-stone-benefits-50x30.jpg 50w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/04\/23101835\/quartz-stone-benefits-150x90.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 940px) 100vw, 940px\" \/><figcaption class=\"wp-element-caption\">Quartz countertop benefits your luxurious kitchen<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"mbgc-slide-caption\"><a href=\"#contactUsModal\" data-toggle=\"modal\"><img decoding=\"async\" class=\"img-fluid\" alt=\"Revive your home with modern and affordable home interiors!\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/02\/09144537\/revive-your-home-with-modern-and-affordable-home-interiors.jpg \" \/><\/a><\/div>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Quartz Stone Price<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Luxurious quartz stone is a bit expensive because it is more visually appealing and offers a range of designs, colours, and patterns to suit every home and preference. Currently, one quartz stone slab costs around 25-30k. However, how much to buy and which one to buy depends significantly on the place, needs, and interior preferences.&nbsp;<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"940\" height=\"564\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/04\/23101824\/quartz-stone-price.jpg\" alt=\"Pricing of quartz stone used in kitchens for every budget\" class=\"wp-image-55862\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/04\/23101824\/quartz-stone-price.jpg 940w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/04\/23101824\/quartz-stone-price-300x180.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/04\/23101824\/quartz-stone-price-768x461.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/04\/23101824\/quartz-stone-price-50x30.jpg 50w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/04\/23101824\/quartz-stone-price-150x90.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 940px) 100vw, 940px\" \/><figcaption class=\"wp-element-caption\">Quartz stone options for every budget!<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Conclusion<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Impressed by the magic of quartz? Investing in your <a href=\"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/interior-design\/\">home interiors<\/a> is a decision not made every day or even every few years! It is wise to invest in things that yield long-term returns. As <a href=\"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/\">interior design experts<\/a>, we are confident that incorporating quartz stone into your home interior project will elevate your living experience, creating a home that symbolises comfort, luxury, and modernity!<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>At <a href=\"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/\">DesignCafe<\/a>, which is present in multiple cities across India, with over 400+ expert designers, a 10-year warranty, and various affordable interior options, <a href=\"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/contact-us\/\">your FREE consultation<\/a> is just a click away!\u00a0Have a nice chat with one of our designers, or step into the nearest <a href=\"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/experience-centre\/\">DesignCafe experience centre<\/a> for a complimentary tour of your dream home! Have a wonderful day.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">FAQs On Use Of Quartz Stone In Interiors<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>Can quartz stone be used for flooring in interior design?<\/strong><br>Yes, quartz stone is an excellent choice for flooring, offering durability and timeless elegance.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>Is quartz stone suitable for high-traffic areas in interior spaces?<\/strong><br>Yes, quartz&#8217;s exceptional durability allows it to thrive in high-traffic areas. Whether it&#8217;s the bustling kitchen or other living spaces, quartz maintains its aesthetic appeal and lasting resilience.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>How does quartz stone perform in terms of scratch and stain resistance?<\/strong><br>Quartz stone boasts remarkable scratch and stain resistance, ensuring a long-lasting and clean kitchen surface. You will get the beauty of quartz without worrying about scratches or stains, even with daily use and occasional spills.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>How does quartz stone compare to granite and marble in terms of durability?<\/strong><br>Quartz stone surpasses both granite and marble in terms of durability. While granite and marble may require sealing and are susceptible to scratches, quartz is non-porous, scratch-resistant, and doesn&#8217;t require sealing.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>Can quartz stone be used for fireplace surrounds or mantels?<\/strong><br>Certainly! Quartz stone is an excellent choice for fireplace surrounds and mantels. Its heat-resistant properties make it ideal for such applications, ensuring both style and functionality.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"row blog-form\">\n\t<div class=\"offset-lg-3 col-lg-6 bg-light\">\n<fieldset class=\"field-set\">\n<!-- <legend align=\"left\"> -->\n                    \n    <h3 class=\"widget-title text-dark text-center mb-0\">Looking For Functional Interior Designs?<\/h3>\n  \n \n     <p class=\"text-center text-dark mt-0\"> Get 20% extra space with smart solutions<\/p>\n    <!-- <\/legend> -->\n<form id=\"blogContactUsFormMain\" action=\"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/get_quote_action.php\" method=\"post\"\n    novalidate=\"novalidate\">\n    <div class=\"form-group\">\n        <input type=\"text\" class=\"form-control\"  name=\"your-name\" placeholder=\"Enter your name*\" \/>\n        <!-- <span class=\"sales-txt-label\" id=\"labeltxt\">Enter your name*<\/span>  -->\n    <\/div>\n    <div class=\"form-row dc-falg-row\">\n        <!-- <div class=\"form-group col-md-3 guideForm\">\n            <select name=\"your-phone-ext\" id=\"id_select2_example\" class=\"id_select2_example drop-downfield form-dropdown\"\n                onfocus='this.size=5;' onblur='this.size=1;' onchange='this.size=1; this.blur();'\n                data-width=\"100%\" data-minimum-results-for-search=\"Infinity\">\n               \n                <option value=\"+01\"\n                    data-img_src=\"https:\/\/media.des